  "imageCount": 4,
  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/492a9d037ac2bb8e.jpg?v=1782525293\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>It's a pretty exciting new year already for all of us at <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/whats-hot/%3Fpp%3D300\">Two Peas in a Bucket</a>, as we are joined by some new talented ladies.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/9d2b44ab77b1fd3d.jpg?v=1782525296\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>So glad I had the unique opportunity last year to visit the Two Peas head office and warehouse.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/94671d381999cbd7.jpg?v=1782525298\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Getting Crafty || copyright Two Peas In a Bucket Really excited about the announcement that there will be videos everyday (Monday-Saturday) featuring various topics. No doubt there will be plenty of inspiration to help you document your awesome life. I will continue to do my 365 photo-a-day project as I found it to be rewarding, fun and pretty easy most days. Even though I didn't finish putting together my monthly collages (and I may not actually ever finish), the groupings of photos were neat to see together.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/3d8efdb7928ff4d8.jpg?v=1782525301\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>This Is My Wonderful Life || Copyright Two Peas In a Bucket Looking forward to being a part of the Garden Girls again this year!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
